\]

\end_inset

נחליף משתנים: 
\begin_inset Formula $\begin{array}{rcl}
x' & = & x-1\\
y' & = & y-4
\end{array}$
\end_inset

 לקבל:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\left(x'\right)^{2}}{5^{2}}+\frac{\left(y'\right)^{2}}{4^{2}}=+1
\]

\end_inset

